M||tx|---
M||name|subagent-driven-dv
M||desc|>-
M||tx|Use when executing implementation plans w/ independent tasks in the current sn
M||vers|1.0.0
M||plat|[]
M||meta|
M||herm|
M||tags|[qa, testing, debugging, qual, lint, code-rv, pulse, productivity]
M||tx|---
M|Suba|Exec|spec compliance rv first, then code qual rv.
M|Suba|**Wh|** You delegate tasks to specialized ag w/ isolated context. By precisely crafting their instructions and context, you ensure they stay focused and succeed at their task. They shd never inherit your sn's context or history — you construct exactly what they need. This also preserves your own context for coordination work.
M|Suba|**Co|** Fresh subagent per task + two-stage rv (spec then qual) = hi qual, fast iteration
